    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c3c59746d384ba18190a6d3"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Your Highness, as you all know, the attackers clearly have access to [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSLDF],SLDF]] grade material but I still think that their overall intentions: to pillage as much as possible before disappearing.\n\nAnd it's unlikely to be a coincidence that they have struck at us at the close down of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAuriganCivilWra],civil war]], as Captain Murray claims.",
      "branches": [
        {
