      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c734ad8b11e3eae80c37436"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "But as for the reports that they will raze nearly everything on the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAuriganReach],Reach]] that is highly doubtful despite what Lord Madeira believes.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
