      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c7777cee50083fd0f2bd0de"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "So does do your [[DM.Factions[faction_InterstellarExpeditions],IE]] sources claim Lord Madeira, but even so the last reported claims date back to the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreFirstSuccessionWar],First]] and [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[Lore2ndSuccessionWar],Second]] Succession Wars.\n\nTheir last sightings were more than a century ago, during the scourging of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreOutworldsAlliance],Outworlds Alliance]].",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
