      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Last known sightings Colonel Haust, since absence of proof is not absence of existence, even if we haven't been able to confirm the claimed razing of the [[DM.Factions[faction_TortugaDominion],Tortuga Dominion]] by the Harbingers as Captain Murray claims.",
