      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c35a9d1604ef27db15580d1"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Very unlikely, even if we could find where they found that gear, most likely from either an abandoned SLDF or [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreRimWorldsRepublic],RWR]] outpost in [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAnteriorSpace],Anterior Space]], most likely in the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreOuterSphere],Outer Sphere]] region.\n\nAnd there are no known habitable star systems past [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreFarhome],Farhome]] according to our records.",
      "branches": [
