    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cce75e4b558b88639f11949"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "To our knowledge, the entire Deep Periphery is empty of habitable worlds past the rimward edge of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHyadesRim],Hyades Rim]], Lady Arano.\n\nFinding them would like searching for a needle in a haystack, even if we had the resources of Interstellar Expeditions or the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreComStarExplorerCorps],Explorer Corps]].",
