        "id": "9c71826e4232b1a0488f6241"
      },
      "index": 10,
      "text": "And regardless of finding them, we are still in need to finish securing [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreCoromodir],Coromodir]] since my uncle is still evading capture, while we need to organize the defense against the Harbingers.",
      "branches": [
