        "id": "9c788c4c751d634488861dfd"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Yes, your Highness, there are still several [[DM.Factions[faction_AuriganDirectorate],Directorate]] loyalists present in the system, so it can take time but our nets are set for when Lord [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSantiagoEspinosa],Espinosa]] attempts to move from his current hiding place.",
