        "id": "9c17d57dd02184bb5b6cef80"
      },
      "index": 12,
      "text": "And even with control of most of the former Directorate's military and the [[DM.Factions[faction_AuriganRestoration],Restoration]]'s resources, you've seen the estimated force numbers that we will be facing, Kamea.\n\nWe will be defeated unless we activate Project REDOUBT.",
